<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.3">
<l>oḻivoṉṟi lātapa lūḻitō ṟūḻi nilāvapōm</l>
<l>vaḻiyait tarunaṅkaḷ vāṉava rīcaṉai niṟkappōy</l>
<l>kaḻiya mikanalla vāṉkavi koṇṭu pulavīrkā</l>
<l>ḷiḻiya karutiyōr māṉiṭam pāṭaleṉ ṉāvatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking very good divine poems, you poets, [only] to go [and] pass,</l>
<l>while our lord stands, the lord of the celestials who gives the way</l>
<l>that goes to last for many aeons after aeons without any end,</l>
<l>what is [the point] of lowly regarding [and] singing a [mere] humanity?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
